And so these are just a few
shots of us on our road trip,

00:27:07.960 --> 00:27:08.650
Gunnar relaxing.

00:27:09.724 --> 00:27:11.640
GUNNAR KARL GISLASON:
There is no place better

00:27:11.640 --> 00:27:14.030
to relax than Icelandic moss.

00:27:15.560 --> 00:27:17.685
JODY EDDY: It's really, I
think, maybe challenging.

00:27:17.685 --> 00:27:20.170
Our photographer, his
name is Evan Sung,

